CONDITION: Point_Singularity
CONDTYPE: over points
CONDMESHTYPE: over nodes
QUESTION: Ungaged_layers#CB#(1,2,3,4,5,6)
VALUE: 1
HELP: Number of ungaged layers around a point:\n- In the regularized formulations, the divergence term of the elements\n   inside the ungauged layers is removed.\n- In the LL2P formulations, both the divergence term and the bubble\n   contribution of the elements inside the ungauged layers are removed.
END CONDITION

