CONDTYPE: over surfaces
CONDMESHTYPE: over face elements
QUESTION: Plasma_wave_type#MAT#(Plasma_far_field_propeties)
VALUE: FW
HELP: Cold plasma wave type at the boundary:\n- FW : n2 = RL/S.\n- RW : n2 = R.\n- LW : n2 = L.\n- PW : n2 = P.
END CONDITION

